snippet.title: Corridor VR - Announce Trailer | PS VR2 Games
snippet.description:
https://store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/10008515

Journey into the Corridor! In 'Corridor VR' players will navigate their way through a branched labyrinth of corridors featuring physics based puzzles and platforming and a unique mirror swap mechanic. The player must use the ability of switching between the "normal" world and the "mirror" world to help overcome the many obstacles that they will face. Navigate deeper and discover the mysteries of the 'Corridor' to save yourself and your captain. 

Coming in 2024, Wishlist now!

#ps5 #psvr2 #psvr2games
